"""
Orca CLI - Batch Inference Orchestrator

Thin HTTP client that talks to the Orca control plane server.
Set ORCA_SERVER env var to point to your control plane (default: http://localhost:26336).

Usage:
    orca deploy <model_name> <input_file> [options]
    orca plan <model_name> <input_file> [options]
    orca progress [job_id]
    orca status
    orca logs <cluster_id>
    orca clusters

Examples:
    orca deploy Qwen/Qwen3-32B demo_batch.jsonl
    orca deploy Qwen/Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct demo_batch.jsonl --slo 4
    orca plan Qwen/Qwen3-32B demo_batch.jsonl
    orca progress
    orca status
"""
